<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<scheme version="2.0" title="Bias in AI Assessment Grading – Unsupervised Analysis | IT9201 MSc AI, Bahrain Polytechnic" description="Unsupervised ML pipeline to detect and analyse demographic bias in AI-powered essay grading using the ASAP-2 dataset. Implements k-Means, PCA and Hierarchical Clustering with Silhouette, t-SNE, Radviz, Box Plot and Distributions for bias auditing. IT9201 – Machine Learning and Data Mining, MSc Artificial Intelligence, Bahrain Polytechnic.">
